{"id": 90, "genre": 1000, "title": "在网上更容易生气，这到底是为什么？", "description": "承认吧，我们在网上会更容易生气，情绪一到，还会骂出各种文采飞扬的脏话。我们本来是温柔的人，是网络让我们变得刻薄，现在是来想想为什么的时候了！", "record_count": 2366, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194626PMNEIp6rwuziofWh.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-09-29T08:20:43Z", "questions": [{"id": 94, "title": "在网上更容易生气，这到底是为什么？", "content": "在网上更容易生气，这到底是为什么？\r\n", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 810, "content": "隐姓埋名给了我嚣张的机会", "image": "img/option/option/201606061618283jCFl4Lo8eh2uZmG.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 811, "content": "脑补太多对方的恶意", "image": "img/option/option/201606061618280XN7CqsdOGa2YtzI.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 812, "content": "说脏话不用罚款", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161828wYdeSi2OMD5u97nk.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 813, "content": "打字比说话思路更清晰", "image": "img/option/option/201606061618290J6eNSabwrkB91fK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 814, "content": "帮腔的人一大堆", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161830vdoPsiW9M21LtCHy.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 815, "content": "没人看到自己那张失态的脸", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193948W2r5aZOFxicVQMUp.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 816, "content": "网络上脑筋不好的人有点多，我忍不住", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161830rs2YILlpqK7yaOVx.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}